  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n    Specifically crafted HTML file with OffscreenCanvas can cause Use After Free of a MemoryManagedPaintCanvas object in OffscreenCanvasRenderingContext2D::DrawTextInternal(). This bug may be exploited to achieve one click remote code execution in  renderer process."
